.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-INVOICE-PAID-AMOUNT-KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-paid-amount-kurtosis \- FEAT-2826 node-invoice-paid-amount-kurtosis
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-paid-amount-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes excess kurtosis of paid invoice amounts (FEAT-2826).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.TP
.B paid_amount_kurtosis
Excess kurtosis (Fisher definition, normal=0) of amount_received_msat from paid invoices.
.TP
.B n
Number of data points used.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
